%H A099586 Vladimir Shevelev, <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/*/http://list.seqfan.eu/oldermail/seqfan/2017-July/017798.html">Coefficient of x^k in ((x+1)^n modulo x^N+1)</a>, seqfan, Thu Jul 20 2017.
